&lt;p&gt;Observational ability to interpret time series waveform data, identify seismic, infrasonic, and hydroacoustic phases, distinguish signals from background noise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A self-starter with excellent oral and written communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience navigating within the Linux environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience running programs in python, Matlab, or other scientific software.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Demonstrated experience with Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, PowerPoint).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
